<h1>Okapied Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>This privacy policy explains how we handle and protect your personal information (PI). This policy may be updated at any time. All PI held by us will be governed by the most reecently updated policy.</p>
<p>This policy sets out:</p>
<ul>
<li>What information we collect.</li>
<li>How we use your information.</li>
<li>Who we share your information with.</li>
<li>How you control and access your information</li>
<li>How we protect your information</li>
</ul>
<p>This policy was last updated on 14 June 2011</p>
<h3>What information we collect</h3>
<p>We collect PI when you create and account with us. The PI we collect about you includes your name,
email address, phone number, and PayPal email address. When you list a property with us, we also collect
the address of the property</p>
<h3>How we use your information</h3>
<p>We use your PI only for the purposes of providing our services and for communicating with you in relation
to our services.</p>
<ul>
<li>Purchasing Okapied products or services. PI collected when you purchase from us is used to deliver
your booking confirmation electronically.</li>
<li>We may contact you about your stay for customer services and feedback purposes</li>
<li>We use details about your booking to post your feedback about your stay on the relevant property page.
We do not include PI in such postings and customers should not include any PI when providing property
feedback for a particular stay. We reserve the right to remove any PI from feedback posted by users.
</li>
</ul>
<h3>Who we share your information with</h3>
<p>We do not disclose PI or information about customer bookings to anyone except in the following circumstances:</p>
<ul>
<li>Hosts. We provide the guest name, telephone number, and email address for each booking made to the relevant host
Hosts require this information for the booking and may use it if they need to contact you about your booking.
You consent to this transfer of PI, whether the host is in Australia or elsewhere.</li>
<li>PayPal. We work with PayPal to enable secure payments for Okapied services. You will be directed to the PayPal
website in order to complete your payment for a booking.</li>
</ul>
<p>We may also use your PI:</p>
<ul>
<li>for purposes necessary or incidental to the provision of services to you;</li>
<li>to communicate with you;</li>
<li>to verify your identity; or</li>
<li>as required or permitted by any law.</li>
</ul>
<h3>How you control and access your information</h3>
<p>Email Address and Phone:</p>
<ul>
<li>If at any time you need to update your email address and phone number, please log into your account and click
on your username.</li>
<li>If you need to update your PayPal email address, you can do this also, however please note in order to receive a 
booking for a property, you must have a valid PayPal email address.</li>
<li>If at any time you want to enquire about and of your PI what we share, please <a href="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/Browse/Contact/list">contact us.</a></li>
</ul>
<h3>How we protect your information</h3>
<p>We take all reasonable steps to protect the PI that we hold from misuse, loss, or unauthorised access,
including by means of firewalls, password access, and secure servers.</p>
<p>We have obtained a digital certificate from GoDaddy.com, Inc.</p>
<p>Our systems are configured with industry standard data encryption technology. When you send PI
to us over the internet, your data is protected by Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology to ensure
safe transmission</p>
